text.tspan: MIDI IN: Via MIDI FeatherWing DIN-5
MIDI OUT: Via MIDI FeatherWing DIN-5
1. CV OUT is 0-5V DIRECT (no op-amp, 5 octaves at 1V/octave)
2. All DAC outputs have 100 ohm series protection
3. TRIG OUT supports V-Trig (DAC) OR S-Trig (transistor)
4. MCP4728 powered by 5V for full 0-5V output range
5. MIDI + OLED + LEDs powered by 3.3V rail
6. Both power rails require proper decoupling (C1,C2 + C9,C10)
